    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has had 8 min, add the <strong>halved green beans</strong> to the tray</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for 7 min further</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
