    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the green beans have had 7 min, remove the tray from the oven and add the <strong>remaining walnuts</strong></p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a final 3 min or until the walnuts are toasted and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk so they don't burn!</p>",
