    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine the <strong>roasted green beans</strong>, <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>spinach</strong>, <strong>toasted walnuts</strong>,<strong> green lentils</strong> and most of the <strong>walnut pesto dressing </strong>(save some for garnish!) in a large bowl – this is your <strong>lentil & walnut pesto salad</strong></p><p>Slice the<strong> cooked chicken</strong> finely</p>",
