      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sliced chicken</strong> with the <strong>lentil & walnut pesto salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>remaining walnut pesto dressing</strong> over the sliced chicken</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
